23/05/2004
BELGRADE, Serbia-Montenegro -- The OSCE mission to Serbia-Montenegro and the Serbian Justice Ministry signed a strategic partnership for democratic reforms of the Serbian judiciary on Friday (21 May). Under the agreement, the OSCE will provide technical assistance and advise the justice ministry on the drafting and implementation of legislative reforms, aimed at bolstering the fight against organised crime. (OSCE Press Release, Tanjug - 21/05/04)
